{"tid":1460724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣唔見晒？","createTime":"2019-08-13T04:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T07:35:04.000Z","uid":135442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9045db5ea36cc57b081474cd04ff5f0861a3d6c8","tid":1460724,"uid":135442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"最近文宣好似消失晒咁好散<br />\n係咪連唔係做前線既文宣都比人拉左要封口？<br />\n我唔係想散播白色恐怖<br />\n我想話比比狗拉左比狗告暴動非法集結同以死明志既手足聽<br />\n你地無做錯核爆都唔割我地亦無忘記你地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日機場同8.18一定要上街</span></span><br />\n用行動證明比世界聽強權愈打壓我地愈要反抗！<br />\n面對不公義既事我地係唔會怕！<br />\n集氣8.18大遊行要多過200萬！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j6Hb6S0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj6Hb6S0.png&h=447de9c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rcPNFc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrcPNFc1.jpg&h=eaee8420&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab8bd99c35f8f9111a57822308fcec62054dda75","tid":1460724,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:34:20.000Z","msg":"尋日俾散水撚玩到咁仲想水人入去哂車錢？"},{"pid":"9d140d9053161cfe9c5a02db4a47802d4dd8e77d","tid":1460724,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:47:46.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以整多少少人神共憤嘅俾遊客<br />\n好多時佢地知 Hong Kong fight for freedom<br />\n但好多時吸睛嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\">殘忍同無恥嘅行為</span><br />\n同埋可以出<span style=\"color: red;\">數字</span><br />\n吸引左佢地再講其他野<br />\n要令佢地覺得我地起<span style=\"color: red;\">人道災難</span>入面<br />\n佢地係於心不忍 而唔係其他國家嘅野唔關佢地事<br />\n<br />\n文宣小妹有野想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲</span>"},{"pid":"ef62dbb6893bf0ed4b6f2e79ae91d969de28ac78","tid":1460724,"uid":135442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab8bd99c35f8f9111a57822308fcec62054dda75","tid":1460724,"uid":49753